♪ Quiet day calms me,
oh, serenity. ♪

7
00:00:57,208 --> 00:01:04,166
♪ Someone, please, tell me. ♪

8
00:01:04,250 --> 00:01:09,791
♪ Oh, mmm, what
is it they say? ♪

9
00:01:09,875 --> 00:01:15,416
♪ Maybe I will know one day. ♪

10
00:01:15,500 --> 00:01:22,416
♪ I don't know what
